This product includes software developed as a research prototype for the
Hack-Nation 6th Global AI Hackathon (Challenge 06 — Genome Firewall).

This software is a research prototype and is NOT a medical device. It must not be
used for clinical decision-making. Every antibiotic-response prediction must be
confirmed by standard laboratory antimicrobial susceptibility testing. See the
DISCLAIMER file.

The system is strictly defensive: it predicts and explains antibiotic resistance
that already exists. It does not design, modify, synthesize, or optimize organisms.
